'''Visqueen''' is a [[power pop]]/[[punk music|punk rock]] band from [[Seattle, Washington]], formed in 2001. It is named after a brand of [[polyethylene]] film that [[United States Secretary of Homeland Security]] [[Tom Ridge]] once recommended as a defense against [[bioterrorism]].
